12 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Look </div><div class="t m280 x50 h5 y28b ff1 fs2 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"> up the following texts. What can we learn from them about how </div><div class="t m281 x51 h5 y28c ff1 fs2 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">we should or should not relate to our parents? </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
